The rules for The Purple Challenge:


1) Click on this link, HOWEVER, YOU CAN NOT READ THE STORY AHEAD OF TIME!
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ClQzUMXRr1qasqJ0k08B8QtosDQzfNHEMVB5D6LQ5S4/edit
2) Record yourself reading the whole story from start to finish with an as little laughing and mistakes as possible

3) You can ONLY use the VERY FIRST TAKE

4) Do not make ANY edits or alterations to the one recording you have

5) Upload it and give the video the name of "The Purple Prince (aka. The Purple Challenge)"
